#

Chickpea and Quinoa Salad with Avocado

25 min
$12
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickEasy

Description

A refreshing salad packed with protein and healthy fats, perfect for a quick lunch or dinner.

Ingredients

  • quinoa: 1 cup
  • chickpeas (canned, drained and rinsed): 1 can
  • avocado: 1
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
